---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="bg-black py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center">Aortic Root Deformation Analysis</h1>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-gray-300 space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg">
          Deformation analysis is a sophisticated computational approach that meticulously quantifies and visualizes structural changes in the aortic root following Transcatheter Aortic Valve Replacement (TAVR) procedures.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">Key Objectives</h2>
        
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Precise Measurement</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2">
            <li>Track deformations across multiple anatomical sections</li>
            <li>Provide comprehensive structural insights</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Computational Methodologies</h3>
          <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-4">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold">Strain Analysis</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Measures material deformation under stress</li>
              <li>Quantifies local and global structural changes</li>
              <li>Provides insights into tissue elasticity and response</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-4">Finite Element Modeling</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Creates detailed computational models</li>
              <li>Simulates structural behavior under different conditions</li>
              <li>Predicts potential long-term structural adaptations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Clinical Significance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Deformation analysis goes beyond simple measurements. It:
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2">
              <li>Supports personalized treatment strategies</li>
              <li>Helps predict potential long-term structural responses</li>
              <li>Enhances understanding of patient-specific anatomical adaptations</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>